The paper discusses feature detectors and descriptors used in computer vision applications, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also proposes a new variant of the repeatability rate, which involves evaluating the performance of algorithms, a topic that is relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves experimentation and evaluation of different algorithms, which is relevant to robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
